border=0 alt="Image by FlamingText.com"></a>
</BODY></HTML></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/bayonaero.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=varulvthewarrior>Varulv the Warrior</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardfellow</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/18/01 9:48:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=598.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmm</span><hr size=1> I think rangers are a good addition to any guild.<br>
<br>
They do alot of damage, which is a very welcome thing in most boss encounters I've been in <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
