 <p><IMG SRC="http://user.tninet.se/~mhf993y/anna/sigfile.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uedeina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edeina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Board Mistress</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/18/01 11:11:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=598.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.one.se/users/chribesk/edeina.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm</span><hr size=1> Actually, ShadowKnight is the only class that is totally unnneeded in the high end game. That class need some saving grace from Verant. Shadowknights are a very good class for single groups, but on raids they are just very weak warriors with a harm touch that won't even put a dent in a velious mobs health and a summon corpse that is never wanted since you have at least one 57+ necro with you for manafeeding anyway. That they are better tanks then rangers do them no good - Warriors with the defensive dicipline are the ONLY tanks anyway.<br>
<br>
Rangers have a harder time to find a group, mostly because of prejudice, but they kick ass on raids. They can often be used as a TrueShot deathsquad, and even in melee they do huge amounts of damage that doesn't have the same aggro management problems as the evade skill of the rouges. (a few rogues is great for damage, but add too many and they will just transfer the aggro back and forth between each other.)<br>
<br>
Plus, Rangers and Paladins are needed for their special buffs.<br>
<br>
Also, Rangers are good enough tanks for most single group encounters. But yes, a warrior/paladin/sk is better at it. In groups, Rangers are perfect as damagedealer+secondary tank+utility class.<br>
<br>
