Your Friendly Forum Gnome<br>
<img src=http://discowliten.homestead.com/files/greatest.gif gif ></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uflexuregraverobber.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Flexure Graverobber</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/18/01 1:05:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=598.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> uhm..</span><hr size=1> Can someone please tell me when rangers have a hard time finding a group?<br>
